Class SetMeal

java.lang.Object
foms.food.FoodItem
foms.food.SetMeal
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class SetMeal extends FoodItem implements Serializable
The `SetMeal` class represents a combination of food items offered as a single meal. It extends the `FoodItem` class and implements the `Serializable` interface.
